class ProstateDataset(torch.utils.data.Dataset):
    def __init__(self, files, masks):
        self.files = files
        self.masks = masks

    def set_tfms(self, tfms):
        self.tfms = tfms
        
    def presize(self, t: TensorDicom3D):
        return ResizeCrop3D(crop_by = (0., 0.15, 0.15), 
                            resize_to = (20, 150, 150), 
                            perc_crop = True)(t)
    
    def apply_tfms(self, t: TensorDicom3D):
        return Pipeline([*self.tfms, 
                         RandomCrop3D((0, 15, 15), (0, 10, 10)), 
                         PseudoColor])(t)
        
    def __getitem__(self, i):
        file =  TensorDicom3D.create(self.files[i]).hist_scaled()
        mask =  TensorDicom3D.create(self.masks[i]).hist_scaled()

        file = self.presize(file)
        mask = self.presize(mask)
        file = self.apply_tfms(file)        
        mask = self.apply_tfms(mask)
        return (file, mask)
    
    def __len__(self): return len(self.files)
    
train_ds = ProstateDataset(sample_data.t2_dcm_path, sample_data.t2_mask_base) 
train_ds.set_tfms(aug_transforms_3d(p_all =.15))
